## Sequencing and Dependencies

The implementation order should be:

1. **`src/analytics.zig`** - add `ini_parse` counter (no dependencies)
2. **`src/interchange/ini.zig`** - the parser (depends only on `bun.ast`, `bun.logger`, `bun.strings`, `std`)
3. **`src/interchange.zig`** - add re-export (depends on ini.zig existing)
4. **`src/bun.js/api/INIObject.zig`** - the binding (depends on interchange/ini.zig)
